ech/article/3261264/tiktok-argues-how-bytedance-protects-children-douyin-irrelevant-youth-addiction-lawsuits-us?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>代表年轻人及其家人的美国律师声称，海外版 TikTok 以美国版所没有的方式保护中国儿童。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 02:10:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3261264/tiktok-argues-how-bytedance-protects-children-douyin-irrelevant-youth-addiction-lawsuits-us?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>首次分享Covid-19基因组数据的中国科学家在实验室关闭之战后引发同情</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3261238/chinese-scientist-who-first-shared-covid-19-genome-data-sparks-sympathy-after-lab-closure-battle?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在母公司医院将张永珍拒之门外后，张永珍在他的上海实验室外扎营，引发了公众的同情和对著名病毒学家所接受治疗的质疑。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 01:00:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3261238/chinese-scientist-who-first-shared-covid-19-genome-data-sparks-sympathy-after-lab-closure-battle?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>乔·拜登因称盟友印度和日本“仇外”和“不想要移民”而面临批评</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3261255/joe-biden-faces-some-criticism-saying-allies-india-japan-are-xenophobic-and-dont-want-immigrants?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>美国总统试图证明，如果各国欢迎移民，经济就会改善，但一些人警告说，他的话是一个外交错误。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 22:19:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3261255/joe-biden-faces-some-criticism-saying-allies-india-japan-are-xenophobic-and-dont-want-immigrants?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国需要“耐心资本”来为其科技发展提供资金。缓慢而稳定地赢得比赛吗？</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3261207/china-wants-patient-capital-fund-its-tech-drive-will-slow-and-steady-win-race?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>分析人士表示，中国政治局在一份官方公报中表示，随着中国转向科技驱动的增长模式，“耐心资本”预计将介入，这显示出急需的对长期的关注。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 22:00:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3261207/china-wants-patient-capital-fund-its-tech-drive-will-slow-and-steady-win-race?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>进步（而不仅仅是利润）如何推动中国的工业发展</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/opinion/china-opinion/article/3261040/how-progress-not-just-profit-drives-chinas-approach-industry?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国的经济政策不是为了破坏世界各地的经济，而是基于远见、效率和规模承诺。脱钩不仅会扰乱供应链，还会在我们持续的气候斗争中增加全球能源转型的成本。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 21:30:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/opinion/china-opinion/article/3261040/how-progress-not-just-profit-drives-chinas-approach-industry?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>情报负责人称中俄在台湾附近举行军事演习迫使美国修改计划</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3261254/china-russia-military-exercises-near-taiwan-force-us-revise-plans-intelligence-chiefs-say?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>国家情报总监艾薇儿·海恩斯表示，联合演习表明“中国肯定希望俄罗斯与他们合作，我们认为[俄罗斯]没有理由不这样做”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 20:47:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3261254/china-russia-military-exercises-near-taiwan-force-us-revise-plans-intelligence-chiefs-say?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>在亚洲，美元走强引发稳定性担忧，疑似利率干预</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3261220/asia-us-dollars-growing-strength-gives-rise-stability-concerns-suspected-rate-intervention?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>分析人士表示，中国央行着眼于人民币稳定，可能会让人民币逐渐贬值，但此举“可能在某种程度上适得其反”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 15:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3261220/asia-us-dollars-growing-strength-gives-rise-stability-concerns-suspected-rate-intervention?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>香港太古公司控股上海医疗保健提供商德达医疗</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/business/article/3261229/hong-kongs-swire-pacific-takes-control-shanghai-healthcare-provider-deltahealth?utm_source=rss_feed</link><d